Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, one of the suspects\NTakanori Genda, admits to the crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the case seems to have closed, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(8% 25)\NRed Horse in the Fire\NCase Solved Part 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.77,0:02:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's already 3:00 pm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll just have to forget about Tropical Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that if we do as you-say, fire could be ignited automatically...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the burn on that light bulb...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could be something that coincidentally got there during the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that trick were to be used...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,any of the three could've done it, couldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The owner of that house\NAkira Morozumi, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:03:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That womanizer Misao Soga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as Ryoko's older sister. Keiko Gondo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,seem to have frequently gone in and out of the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came to Mr. Genda's house to find out who the culprit is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so let's hurry and go into the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We may find a diary or something that could be a key to the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you don't even have a search wainrant, and-yet you have-the keys-It's amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told Genda that\NI would prove his innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he broke out in tears and lent it to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure is a big house for\NMr. Genda to be living in alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was living here with his mother after his father passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but last year his mother also passed away of an illness...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way. Mouri,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,did you notice the shoe marks in the corridor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they're here and there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the shoe marks of someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are Mr. Gendas shoe marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same as the shoes that's in the shoes cabinet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that... Mr. Genda...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something strange in the waste basket!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soiled socks and a burnt shirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Mr. Genda's sleepwalking habit was getting worse, maybe his saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other me did it", is not all that much of a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not that kind of a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not the kind of man that would set fire to other people's houses...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuminaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come here a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the telephone bill that wD on top of the shoes cabinet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:05:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It says 30.000 yen a month!\NIsn't it a bit too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that it's strange for a guy who's living alone but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran also talks to Sonoko for a long time over silly things
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the bill totals to about that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,silly Kazuha does the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She talks for a long time with mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why women like to talk on the phone so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well. I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That our phone calls are so silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hopi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you guys were eavesdropping from the front door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't do something\NIow class like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fool!
