Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Radio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,=Itvs inside this vase!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a wiretap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,exactly the same as the vase that is in the front entrance of the Morozumi's, isn't its?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We heard other things too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something about the wastebasket
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's got be one near this waste basket too, a wiretap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? A crystal ball...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time inside the cushion under the crystal ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:40.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've seen that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the crystal of good luck that the woman fortune-teller
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:46.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,at the building in front of Haido Station is selling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:50.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's known for being pretty good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! That small cushion...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a different color but similar to the one\NRyoko was holding, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be in here too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a wiretap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:19.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, something else has come out instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iithe guyfGenda-confessed.\NBut suddenly refused to say anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The red horse was indeed hand-made by Genda...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, he refuses to say anything about the serial arsons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, we're at Gendafs, house right now.\NBut can't find any vital evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genda saying that he has a habit of sleepwalking is probably a lie too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the forensic officers will be here tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I'm sure something will come out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When something more concerning the investigations: come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll contact you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:07:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whew...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it okay, sonny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just great. Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... what are you up to anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making fake calls like that to all three suspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fake calls?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're fake calls, aren't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found wiretaps in the vase at the front entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as well as something in the cushion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is proof everywhere that Mr. Genda had a habit of sleepwalking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... I'll explain everything later...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And us being here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Won't that make more work for the forensic officers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure our hair is on the floor somewhere too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what should we do to erase all evidence that we were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hat should we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go all out and clean the place, what else?
